data.description: 3 Bedrooms / 2 Full Baths with master en suite. Tons of upgrades and move-in ready! NEW IN 2019: Roof, exterior & interior paint, garage doors, kitchen stainless appliances, countertops, light fixtures, bathroom vanities, shower heads, faucets, bathtub, shower, laminate flooring throughout home, interior and exterior doors, vinyl windows. Enjoy the living area with an open floor plan and vaulted ceiling. The new 600sf patio deck is perfect for entertaining or lounging. Big backyard for family, friends, pets. Located on a quiet cul de sac with little through-traffic. Close to schools and shopping.
